Staging area for PixelLab-generated assets awaiting user review.

Files here are NOT loaded by PreloadScene.ts — they live here until the user
approves them, at which point the `pixellab-assets` skill moves them to their
final location under `public/assets/sprites/` or `public/assets/tilesets/`.

Preview staged assets in the browser while the dev server is running:
  http://localhost:5173/assets/_staging/<category>/<asset>/
